{"tid":2002722,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「香港」再出發係黃色組織，唔係「中国香港」再出發","createTime":"2020-05-05T10:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T11:25:36.000Z","uid":126621,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"48663e7b890f5ddaa147426ca514677fe26de3a6","tid":2002722,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"誠哥做主導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n梁振英係on9 扮代表無權力<br />\n爭就業免青年人投閒置散點會係藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁振英：爭就業免青年人投閒置散<br />\n<br />\n梁振英表示，香港陷入困局，「病向淺中醫」，暴力事件減少、肺炎疫情暫緩的今日，是部署、推動「香港再出發」的好時機。他稱大聯盟討論後會公布具體工作計劃，大聯盟的工作包括振興經濟，<span style=\"color: gold;\">為青年人爭取就業、實習和培訓的機會，避免長時間投閒置散</span>；另會支持和配合特區政府持續做好防疫抗疫工作，周六（9日）開始會派發400萬個兒童口罩，也會派發600萬個成人口罩。<br />\n<br />\n踢走廢老藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd00b010710a83fbbc66695ed71e5dcfe9266a9","tid":2002722,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:55:32.000Z","msg":"成功爭取梁振英讓步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc75ddca8ea3254dd9f7b08e55cb236731ee67ae","tid":2002722,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:56:11.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azrnqT2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FazrnqT2.png&h=8254c0b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MikCZd3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMikCZd3.png&h=e597ce85&s={